Shoes are unobtainable items used to detail the shoe selection in Yrsa's Shoe Store's interface.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
9 March 2022
(update)
  • The original shoes were graphically updated.
  • The male basic grey shoe was renamed from "Shoe."{sic} to "Shoe".
26 January –
27 June 2005
  • The items were renamed from "Dummy shoe1" to "Shoe".
  • The items' examines were changed from undefined ("It's a Dummy shoe1.") to "A shoe."
